49:15.928 --> 49:27.326
Because really, if you knew him in 74 or 75, right after, soon after he buzzed, you were one of the few people at that time who knew he was building a major collection.

49:27.346 --> 49:33.375
Now, he was dealing heavily with John Fleming in New York and Warren Howell on the West Coast.

49:34.064 --> 49:42.592
